  <section class="section" id="concepts">\
    <div class="sec-eyebrow">Video concepts</div>\
    <h2 class="sec-title">5 high-retention concepts</h2>\
    <p class="sec-sub">Each concept uses the same structural mechanic: visual confusion \uc0\u8594  satisfying clarity. The problem is shown viscerally before Jumper arrives as the resolution. Select 2\'963 for production.</p>\
\
    <div class="grid-2">\
\
      <div class="card">\
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:.75rem;">\
          <span class="concept-num">01</span>\
          <span class="badge badge-green">Hero awareness</span>\
        </div>\
        <div class="card-title">The Airport with No Signs</div>\
        <div class="card-body mt-1">An international airport \'97 dozens of terminals, no signs, no directions. A traveler spins, passport in hand, completely lost. Then a single path lights up underfoot, leading directly to the gate.</div>\
        <div class="quote-block mt-2">\
          <div class="quote-text" style="font-size:.95rem;">"That's Jumper. Any token. Any chain. One route."</div>\
          <div class="quote-sub">Analogy: Google Maps for your crypto.</div>\
        </div>\
        <div class="tag-strip mt-2"><span class="tag">30s</span><span class="tag">Awareness</span><span class="tag">All segments</span></div>\
      </div>\
\
      <div class="card">\
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:.75rem;">\
          <span class="concept-num">02</span>\
          <span class="badge badge-blue">Earn feature</span>\
        </div>\
        <div class="card-title">The Chef Who Shops at 12 Markets</div>\
        <div class="card-body mt-1">A chef running between 12 grocery markets \'97 sweating, losing ingredients, late. That's every DeFi user managing yield manually. Then one supplier delivers everything optimised. The chef just cooks.</div>\
        <div class="quote-block mt-2">\
          <div class="quote-text" style="font-size:.95rem;">"Jumper Earn. Your yield, personalised and ready."</div>\
          <div class="quote-sub">Show the "For You" feed: wallet activity, risk appetite, idle assets.</div>\
        </div>\
        <div class="tag-strip mt-2"><span class="tag">30s</span><span class="tag">Earn feature</span><span class="tag">Segment A</span></div>\
      </div>\
\
      <div class="card">\
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:.75rem;">\
          <span class="concept-num">03</span>\
          <span class="badge badge-purple">Security trust</span>\
        </div>\
        <div class="card-title">The Monster in the Middle</div>\
        <div class="card-body mt-1">Two hands reaching across a gap \'97 a dark void between them eating dollar signs. Bridges have been crypto's most-hacked layer. The void shrinks. Hands connect. Route shown with fees and security flags.</div>\
        <div class="quote-block mt-2">\
          <div class="quote-text" style="font-size:.95rem;">"Jumper finds the safest, cheapest route \'97 automatically."</div>\
          <div class="quote-sub">Show audit badges. Reinforce: 4\'d7 audited by Spearbit, Code4rena, Quantstamp.</div>\
        </div>\
        <div class="tag-strip mt-2"><span class="tag">30s</span><span class="tag">Security</span><span class="tag">Segment B</span></div>\
      </div>\
\
      <div class="card">\
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:.75rem;">\
          <span class="concept-num">04</span>\
          <span class="badge badge-amber">Idle capital</span>\
        </div>\
        <div class="card-title">Your Money Is Sleeping</div>\
        <div class="card-body mt-1">Dollar bills tucked under a pillow, snoring. Alarm goes off \'97 nothing moves. Then the money wakes up, floats into vaults. Numbers climbing: 80%, 50%, 350% APY. Honest framing \'97 not hype, just opportunity.</div>\
        <div class="quote-block mt-2">\
          <div class="quote-text" style="font-size:.95rem;">"Jumper Earn. Your idle capital shouldn't be sleeping."</div>\
          <div class="quote-sub">Reference live pools: Yearn USDC 80% APY, Spectra vbUSDC 350% APY.</div>\
        </div>\
        <div class="tag-strip mt-2"><span class="tag">30s</span><span class="tag">Earn / yield</span><span class="tag">Segment A + B</span></div>\
      </div>\
\
      <div class="card" style="grid-column: 1 / -1;">\
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:.75rem;">\
          <span class="concept-num">05</span>\
          <span class="badge badge-gray">Portfolio feature</span>\
        </div>\
        <div class="card-title">The Scoreboard You Never Knew Existed</div>\
        <div class="card-body mt-1">A sports fan watching a game \'97 scoreboard blank. No stats, no score. Just vibes. Most portfolio trackers let you watch. Jumper Portfolio lets you act: live positions, cross-chain, in/out buttons, yield visible.</div>\
        <div class="quote-block mt-2">\
          <div class="quote-text" style="font-size:.95rem;">"Jumper Portfolio. Stop watching. Start playing."</div>\
          <div class="quote-sub">Analogy: the difference between watching chess on TV and actually moving the pieces. Show Portfolio UI with direct deposit/withdrawal capability.</div>\
        </div>\
        <div class="tag-strip mt-2"><span class="tag">30s</span><span class="tag">Portfolio feature</span><span class="tag">Segment A</span></div>\
      </div>\
